OL,3,GGrampian
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FMostly cloudy in the morning
OL,6,Fwith occasional, mainly light rain.
OL,7,FMainly dry in the afternoon with some
OL,8,Fsunshine breaking through but a few
OL,9,Flight showers are still possible in
OL,10,FMoray.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FSome light rain returning to
OL,13,FMoray and the West this evening then
OL,14,Fbecoming dry with some clear periods
OL,15,Fdeveloping overnight.
OL,16,
OL,17,CTuesday:FA sunny start then turning
OL,18,Fcloudier from the west. Some patchy
OL,19,Flight rain developing but some areas
OL,20,Fstaying dry. Windy with some rain
OL,21,Fovernight.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
