OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:
OL,6,FWednesday bright with sunny spells and
OL,7,Fa few showers. Cloudy with rain on
OL,8,FThursday, some heavy later. Then
OL,9,Fbrighter again on Friday with sunny
OL,10,Fintervals and a few showers.
